.RS 2
.TP 2
.B
\fIundefined_function_calls\fR\&(*):
Returns a list of calls to \fBundefined functions\fR\&\&.
.TP 2
.B
\fIundefined_functions\fR\&:
Returns a list of \fBundefined functions\fR\&\&. 
.TP 2
.B
\fIlocals_not_used\fR\&(*):
Returns a list of local functions that have not been locally used\&.
.TP 2
.B
\fIexports_not_used\fR\&:
Returns a list of exported functions that have not been externally used\&.
.TP 2
.B
\fIdeprecated_function_calls\fR\&(*):
Returns a list of external calls to \fBdeprecated functions\fR\&\&.
.TP 2
